listFile examples

These examples show how listFile should work on the birds and fish lists provided with the starter code.

In []:
listFile('birds.txt')

Prints
1 tern
2 albatross
3 seagull
4 sparrow
5 cardinal
6 oriole
7 robin
8 swallow
9 stork
10 cassowary
11 ostrich
12 chicken
13 tanager
14 goose
15 turkey
16 quail
17 chickadee
18 nuthatch


In []:
listFile('fish.txt')

Prints
1 tuna
2 swordfish
3 sawfish
4 sunfish
5 mackerel
6 anchovy
7 flying fish
8 angler fish
9 lantern fish
10 salmon
11 carp
12 catfish
